title: Coyote Cafe
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A theme restaurant offering Mexican cuisine. Burrito and enchilada filled with roasted vegetable, salsa, guacamole, Mexican rice, and served with a salad; vegans ask to omit sour cream and cheese. Weekends the burritos and enchilada plates cannot be altered for vegans, so only available Mon-Fri. Vegans can get the Italian dressing, mixed salad & coyote salad (ask to omit egg) and potato chips.
